data.description: FANTASTIC Mid City Home with New Roof and Siding has it all. 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, wood floors, high ceilings, open kitchen and living space as you step from the front porch into this Lovely home. Off street parking with rear yard access.  Have your own Happy Hour on balcony w/views overlooking city skyline. Newer A/C & Foundation, Solar Panels, Upper 2 bedrooms & bath have separate entrance available for possible Rental opportunities. Low Flood ins. Easy access to Medical Corridor-Lafitte Greenway-Streetcar & French Quarter.  This unique home offers an ideal location for those seeking the best of New Orleans living.
